1. scan for nearby devices
$ hcitool scan --refresh

2. change passcodes in /var/lib/bluetooth/{MAC address}/pincodes

3. configure rfcomm device with
$ vim /etc/bluetooth/rfcomm.conf

4. restart the bluetooth daemon
$ sudo /etc/init.d/bluetooth restart

5.Bind bluetooth devices to corresponding channels
sudo rfcomm bind all
sudo rfcomm bind #
